As Kubernetes is the de facto container deployment and management tool, its workloads must be regularly monitored and secured with appropriate security implementations.

Security professionals use tools such as Advanced Cluster Security for Kubernetes, Aqua Kubernetes Security, and Kyverno to secure the Kubernetes environment.

â–ª Advanced Cluster Security for Kubernetes
Advanced Cluster Security (ACS) for Kubernetes is a comprehensive solution designed to enhance the security of Kubernetes environments. 

It also helps build, deploy, and run cloud-native applications.

It provides a robust set of tools and features focused on visibility, compliance, threat detection, and risk management to ensure comprehensive protection for cloud-native workloads

